                            <comment id="12834896" author="kzhang" created="Wed, 17 Feb 2010 17:59:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s not easy to write a unit test since the bug depends on a race condition among RPC handler threads. But we have run the same manual tests with the patch and the errors disappeared.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12835654" author="devaraj" created="Fri, 19 Feb 2010 09:00:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12835659" author="devaraj" created="Fri, 19 Feb 2010 09:05:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just committed this. Thanks, Kan!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12835663" author="hudson" created="Fri, 19 Feb 2010 09:22:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Hadoop-Common-trunk-Commit #177 (See &lt;a href=&quot;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Hadoop-Common-trunk-Commit/177/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Hadoop-Common-trunk-Commit/177/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    . Makes sure that SASL encryption and push to responder queue for the RPC response happens atomically. Contributed by Kan Zhang.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
